 own party originally set this whole thing up. Meanwhile, everyday Aussies are just hoping their extra dollars can at least cover one overpriced grocery trip.', 0, 'factabot', 'Labors Tax Cuts Pass Lower HouseCoalition Begins Mourning Period', 'draft', NULL, NULL, '2025-03-28 11:23:39', '2025-03-28 11:23:39', 0);
